name: Fierce
description: A roar rises from the bottom part of a heart. The eyes analyze and scream. Protect the life she love so much, protect her home, her wild nature; it creeps through the undergrowth like a black panther. Poor deluded one who tries to invade her territory, to commit atrocious acts in front of her, to try to take advange... because she will defend all with merciless claws and teeth... //   Self-portrait, 2020 /  4960 x 6200 px / 300 dpi
